Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Transformers: Prime
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo, Optimus!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may wish to save your strength for the main event!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find Fowler and get these kids outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault that we're stuck in this intensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking, Miko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know math when I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is one serious equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this was just an average day with the Autobots,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I don't wanna be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mindless agenda resulted in the disabling of my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the delay of my plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron's building a Space Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to bring through his conquering army.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the only place Megatron could recruit that many fallen warriors...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.92,0:01:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot allow Megatron to send Dark Energon through his Space Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the dead of Cybertron will rise,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,swarm through his vortex,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and invade Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bending human kind to Megatron's twisted rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Nice bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Arcee, really, Miko already tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Tell Optimus I respect him big time. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}if you're at war with the Decepticons,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing I can do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus didn't send me, and no one's asking for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Ok, so if we both agree that I'm not warrior material...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Jack, I just lost someone I cared about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Maybe it's the grief talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe you're growing on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is, I'm just not ready to say good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Optimus, I've pinpointed the location of Megatron's Space Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}High in Earth's orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of our reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, so you guys don't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can't you just Ground Bridge there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}A Ground Bridge has limited range.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Stretch all the way into the orbited vortex could snap
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and scatter us to the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Megatron is likely already in transit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid we must take that risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reaching the Space Bridge first, is our only means of stopping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guess who's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autobots, prepare for departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Space? I... I thought they didn't have any way to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, be seeing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, if you leave me stranded on a planet teeming with humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we meet again, old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autobots, roll out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum overdrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autobots, transform
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and gravitise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look down, or up, or left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Megatron's packing enough Dark Energon to raise Cybertron's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since we don't possess ready means of disabling the Space Bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing gets in or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hahaha... Optimus Prime never disappoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, Starscream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need for concern, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soundwave is locking on to Cybertron's coordinates
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,per my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what are they waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that the Decepticons have sustained serious damage to their inter-stellar navigation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's my handy work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, Bulkhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without the dish,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron will be unable to aim the Space Bridge at Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't the Decepticons know where their own planet is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Cybertron is many light years away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To reach their target, their aim must be astronomically precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Megatron went to the trouble of rendezvousing with his Space Bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have an alternate targeting system.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A remote one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I know of Earth technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt there would exist a single radio telescope dish on this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,powerful enough to pinpoint Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about a whole bunch of linked radio telescope dishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the giant size array in Texas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit back... this is not a child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thinking, Raf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, have Agent Fowler alert the array's stuff to the security hazard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're out of uniform. Put on some pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That maybe a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get passed the array's firewalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... actually think you could keep the Decepticons out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... if I could get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait. Raf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if we could get you... all the way in? Like "inside the building" in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can login to their internal network on the other side of the firewall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The risk is too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Decepticons will be there. Perhaps even on site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, with all due respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you said that yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is bigger than the safety of three humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if we let the Cons win,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're fragged along with everyone else on our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raf?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, Lord Megatron,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Autobots are up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Starscream?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the welcoming committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That'll take some getting used to.\N - Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Security sure is lack in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so are the Decepticons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schematics, with the same alien math we saw on their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, I can download it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be the Space Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Decepticons are synching it to the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can synch to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will they know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the Decepticons see that I'm in the system,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll have no idea I'm in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Decepticons are locking on to Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Megatron, the Space Bridge is ready for activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're locked on to Cybertron, but not for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, Bumblebee,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this can only be Raf's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starscream, what is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soundwave, what is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dishes are heading back towards Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just undo that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens when the Cons realize to being punked?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only virtual combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, like online gaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Jack, what are the Cons gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably like a thousand miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let them lock on again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You handed in an axe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cut the hard line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dishes are locked on to Cybertron...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Starscream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arise, my legion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do we beat a whole planet of the undead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm registering a rapidly expanding mass in their Space Bridge vortex,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one with a peculiar energy signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Energon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, we must destroy the Space Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's enough live energon coursing through it, to achieve detonation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we lack the fire power to ignite it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew how the Space Bridge was engineered,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might find a technical way of accomplishing at feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, will schematics help?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, I must say,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Space Bridge is our sole hope of ever returning to Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain its destruction is the only option?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then by all means,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let us light our darkest hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autobots, take your positions,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and follow Ratchet's lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I make my stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fellow Autobots are wise, Optimus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They know when to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hold no illusions about engaging your army, Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I might derail its objective...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by removing its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Highly and likely Optimus,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I am infused with their very might!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One shall stand, one shall fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things are getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, we're in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcee, pay close attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starscream, what is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not wish to question your all-seeing wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I believe the Autobots are up to something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath your bridge, this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, misdirection, Optimus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would have made a fine Decepticon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I chose my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starscream, my army approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rendezvous with the Space Bridge for pickup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:17:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now follow the line from the flow regulator to the energon pump.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a valve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. To turn all that power against itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all you need do is reverse the current.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Current reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ready the Ground Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starscream! Where is my ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would never make it, Lord Megatron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a fool! Take flight and retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, the Ground Bridge is ready and waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autobots, jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My legion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decepticons, it is with deep sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I note for the log...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron's spark has been extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All... hail... Starscream!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you... think they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four life signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One very faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bulkhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost one this week,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the Allspark, don't let it be two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcee...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other motorcycles in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're my first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Megatron?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even he could've survived Ground Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prime!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get to thank you, but for the save,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is this the part where you say good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and tell us we need to forget we ever saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without the means of leaving this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:21:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we Autobots take strength in the bonds we have forged with our three young friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True warriors,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if not in body,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then in spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Optimus Prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I send this message:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though we did no choose to be of earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would seem that we are here to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you approach this planet with hostile intent,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,know this:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will defend ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will defend humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.98,0:21:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will defend our home.
